ActCanadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
PrecisEnactment of the OFF-ROAD COMPRESSION-IGNITION ENGINE EMISSION REGULATIONS which introduce exhaust emission standards for compression-ignition engines (diesel engines) used in off-road mobile applications such as construction, farming, forestry and mining machinery, beginning in the 2006 model year.
